Lines.3fecd41f-9ae1-6767-f842-92fb29b502a3: Thank you for suggesting this. With only you can I be without pretense.
Lines.0637cef2-f373-9ebb-8c3c-7b376495064b: Beautiful, isn't it? One day, this world will be our home again. We broke a Netherbrain - we can break Zariel's hold on you.
Lines.540a9844-6424-cc96-4717-84d039bec81b: I should have known you would notice that being around others fatigues me.
Lines.84c7d853-c4e4-2360-d9bc-303dc23fefdb: Beautiful, isn't it? Those stars once guided my journeys across the sea... and now you are the brightest light of all.
Lines.93c0f0a1-d980-c760-b746-9691df7d37eb: You know... every time you call me that...
Lines.0ddcda73-b5f0-a29d-c5e7-458a1738ea4e: Why don't we sit here for a while... and bask in each other's company? We can return to the party when we are ready.
